#
# Build-context filter for CubeOps/Dockerfile (context = repository root).
# The repo-root .dockerignore excludes everything except docker/ builder files,
# so CubeOps and its sibling CubeDB dependency must be explicitly allowed here.
**
!CubeOps
!CubeOps/**
!CubeDB
!CubeDB/**
!cubelog
!cubelog/**
